{
  "title": "Ground Croatian Lamb Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and earthy stew featuring ground lamb, bay leaf, and traditional Croatian spices, perfect for a weeknight dinner. This halal-friendly dish is made with pressure cooking for a tender and flavorful meal.",
  "cuisine": "Croatian",
